headline: Marriott International Announces Release Date For Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings
summary: Marriott International, Inc. (Nasdaq: MAR) will report fourth quarter 2025 earnings results on Tuesday, February 10, 2026, at approximately 7:00 a.m. Eastern Time (ET). The company will hold a conference call for the investment community on Tuesday, February 10, 2026, at 8:30 a.m. (ET). Marriott International's President and Chief Executive Officer, Anthony Capuano, and Chief Financial Officer and Executive Vice President, Development, Leeny Oberg, will discuss the company's performance.

headline: Marriott appoints new executives as leadership shuffle continues
summary: The company is filling roles set to be vacated by two long-time leaders bound for retirement in March.
